'''green tea'''

#Leaves of the [[tea]] plant which are treated with [[steam]] or [[roast]]ed to [[denature]] the [[enzyme]]s that cause the leaves to darken and change taste. (Without this step they would become [[oolong tea]] or [[black tea]]).
#A beverage brewed from green tea leaves.



